Package: sbackup
Architecture: all
Depends: sbackup-common(= ${binary:Version}),
         sbackup-gtk(= ${binary:Version}),
         python ( >= 2.5 ), python (<< 3.0),
         ${misc:Depends}
Description: (Not So) Simple Backup Suite for desktop use
 (Not So) Simple Backup Suite comprises of backend backup script and
 GNOME GUI frontends that provide a simple yet powerful backup
 solution for common desktop users.
 .
 Backups can be written to local directories or remote servers using
 GIO/GVFS technology. A fine control is possible regarding what
 folders and files to backup. Files can be excluded even with a set
 of regular expressions. Regular backups can be scheduled.
 .
 This meta package installs required packages to use (Not So) Simple Backup
 Suite.
 
Package: sbackup-common
Architecture: all
Depends: python ( >= 2.5 ), python (<< 3.0),
         ${misc:Depends},
         python-gobject,
         gvfs
Conflicts: sbackup
Description: (Not So) Simple Backup Suite core functionality
 (Not So) Simple Backup Suite common files package. This package contains
 the minimum set of files to create backups from the commandline. It uses
 GIO/GVFS for access of remote backup destinations.

Package: sbackup-gtk
Architecture: all
Depends: sbackup-common(= ${binary:Version}),
         python ( >= 2.5 ), python (<< 3.0),
         ${misc:Depends},
         python-glade2,
         python-gtk2 (>= 2.10),
         python-gnome2,
         python-gobject,
         python-notify,
         menu
Description: (Not So) Simple Backup Suite GTK+ graphical user interface
 (Not So) Simple Backup Suite graphical user interface (GUI) written in 
 GTK+. This package installs the GTK+ GUI of (Not So) Simple Backup Suite
 including a status indicator placed in panel when running backups.

Package: sbackup-ftp
Architecture: all
Depends: sbackup-common(= ${binary:Version}),
         python ( >= 2.5 ), python (<< 3.0),
         ${misc:Depends},
         fuse-utils,
         curlftpfs
Description: (Not So) Simple Backup Suite FTP FUSE plugins
 (Not So) Simple Backup Suite plugins that use FUSE file systems. This
 optional package enables storage of backups on FTP/SFTP locations
 using FUSE.
 .
 Please note, that the core package already enables remote access by means of
 GIO/GVFS. This package is required only in case of explicit need
 for mounting external sites using CURLFTPFS.

Package: sbackup-ssh
Architecture: all
Depends: sbackup-common(= ${binary:Version}),
         python ( >= 2.5 ), python (<< 3.0),
         ${misc:Depends},
         fuse-utils,
         sshfs,
         python-pexpect
Description: (Not So) Simple Backup Suite SSH FUSE plugins
 (Not So) Simple Backup Suite plugins that use FUSE file systems. This
 optional package enables storage of backups on SSH locations
 using FUSE.
 .
 Please note, that the core package already enables remote access by means of
 GIO/GVFS. This package is required only in case of explicit need
 for mounting external sites using SSHFS.

